  "title": "refactor(lodash): remove find usage",
  "body": "This removes all `lodash/find` usages. We need to be careful with `undefined` collections being loop over since Lodash used to deal with that for us.\r\n\r\nNote that we already use `Array.prototype.find` in the codebase and that we document [using a polyfill to support browsers](https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/installation/js/#browser-support).",
